[30;1m44 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m45 | [0m[35mTo avoid extracting irrelevant features, the *TSFRESH* package has a built-in filtering procedure.[0m
[30;1m46 | [0m[35mThis filtering procedure evaluates the explaining power and importance of each characteristic for th[0m
[30;1m47 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m48 | [0m[35mIt is based on the well developed theory of hypothesis testing and uses a multiple test procedure.[0m
[30;1m49 | [0m[35mAs a result the filtering process mathematically controls the percentage of irrelevant extracted fea[0m

[30;1m52 | [0m[35mWhat can't we do with tsfresh?[0m
[30;1m53 | [0m[35m------------------------------[0m
[30;1m54 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m10 | [0m[35mThis is the documentation of **tsfresh**.[0m
[30;1m11 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m12 | [0m[35mtsfresh is a python package.[0m
[30;1m13 | [0m[35mIt automatically calculates a large number of time series characteristics, the so called features.[0m
[30;1m14 | [0m[35mFurther the package contains methods to evaluate the explaining power and importance of such charact[0m
[30;1m15 | [0m[35mregression or classification tasks.[0m
[30;1m16 | [0m[35m[0m
